<link href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=12053&amp;p=137777#p137777"/>
<title type="html"><![CDATA[Re: Graphics - Tools]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=12053&amp;p=137777#p137777"><![CDATA[
When you import in NESST, it will select the closest colour from the currently selected palette. So... use those 4 colours (or make a palette that matches your image and select that). This is explained in the readme.txt that comes with it, by the way, if you haven't taken a look in there.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=5165">rainwarrior</a> — Thu Dec 18, 2014 11:23 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
