<id>http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=12053&amp;p=137757#p137757</id>
<link href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=12053&amp;p=137757#p137757"/>
<title type="html"><![CDATA[Re: Graphics - Tools]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=12053&amp;p=137757#p137757"><![CDATA[
To change the attributes, turn of &quot;apply tiles&quot; but leave &quot;apply palettes&quot; on (toggle &quot;attr checker&quot; if you want to view just the attributes). I say it's quick because the attribute table is just 16 x 15 entries, so should only take a few seconds to fill it in by hand.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=5165">rainwarrior</a> — Thu Dec 18, 2014 5:22 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
